text: læa meux mi phyantray hnung prasb kæ phwk cea thang «thi phwk cea di hı prasb kæ phwk khea ma læw thung sxng thea hæng phyantray nan phwk cea k yang klaw wa sing ni ma cak hin kranan hrux? Cng klaw theid(muhammad) wa man ma cak thi taw khxng phwk than xeng thæ cring xallxh pen phuthrng dechanuphaph henux thuksingthukxyang
